name: Bā - Turn Angst into Art
description: On the peak of first NFT wave in March, someone who sells very well was angry with others who don't. We made a little correction to his statement turning it into an art. Only 88 Editions available, "Eight" is 八 - in Asian culture it means "Happiness". Take this peace for free only when you feel you need it. Please 1 piece at hand, leave Happiness for others too.
